{"tid":501143,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】氣溫急降，不如一齊屠龍取暖? Day159 16/12【MHP2G】","createTime":"2017-12-16T14:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T18:05:35.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b11e04a560f7bdae5cb67656683200ce98ccb8de","tid":501143,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:00:38.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚10點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=C0HKt4MF2W2ykmPSQtzfJZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f9a90572\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=C0HKt4MF2W2ykmPSQtzfJZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=42326f85\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"01c948b2bc30e32a3cdc1f8938276f5422b4aead","tid":501143,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:07:36.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27550bcf636141b9f62521fa4ab36eb36c1f12f8","tid":501143,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c927a50045c3ac312b523d1b59a47b5337403d","ti